1
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:01,534
Alright, Bai Xing, you're up.

2
00:00:05,271 --> 00:00:06,473
I'm in love with you.

3
00:00:06,473 --> 00:00:08,274
I love every part of you.

4
00:00:17,083 --> 00:00:18,618
You can like me all you want,

5
00:00:19,386 --> 00:00:20,987
but you're not in my league.

6
00:00:23,823 --> 00:00:24,824
Because...

7
00:00:26,693 --> 00:00:28,762
I'm willing to give you everything.

8
00:00:30,397 --> 00:00:31,498
Well, I don't want it.

9
00:00:32,565 --> 00:00:33,933
What's your "everything" even worth?

10
00:00:46,513 --> 00:00:47,914
Okay, great.

11
00:00:47,914 --> 00:00:49,115
Let's wrap it up there.

12
00:00:49,115 --> 00:00:49,983
Thank you, thank you.

13
00:00:49,983 --> 00:00:50,950
Thank you, Bai Xing.

14
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:52,352
Thank you, Shasha.

15
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:53,353
Thanks.

16
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,128
We're going to

17
00:01:02,128 --> 00:01:03,696
have a word with the managers.

18
00:01:03,696 --> 00:01:05,432
The three of you, please wait here.

19
00:01:06,166 --> 00:01:07,834
Managers, if you could...

20
00:01:14,808 --> 00:01:16,042
Let's talk.

21
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:32,892
I'm going to the restroom.

22
00:01:36,262 --> 00:01:37,230
Me too.

23
00:01:51,911 --> 00:01:53,313
You're coming with me?

24
00:01:53,613 --> 00:01:54,681
Shouldn't you stay here

25
00:01:54,681 --> 00:01:56,349
with your senior?

26
00:01:56,549 --> 00:01:57,283
Let's go.

27
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,651
Why are you just standing there?

28
00:02:01,663 --> 00:02:03,331
Then let me go!

29
00:02:03,356 --> 00:02:04,290
Oh.
